	  src/Polyhedron.inlines.hh (1.91): In
	  Polyhedron::map_dimensions(const PartialFunction&), the method
	  PartialFunction::maps() is now called at most `n' times, where
	  `n' is the dimension of the vector space enclosing the
	  polyhedron.

