2002-10-14 Monday 16:01  Roberto Bagnara <bagnara@cs.unipr.it>

	* NEWS (1.45), interfaces/C/ppl_c.cc (1.49), interfaces/C/ppl_c.h
	  (1.49), interfaces/Prolog/pl_check.pl (1.26),
	  interfaces/Prolog/ppl_prolog.icc (1.68),
