	* TODO (1.12): More things to do after the merge with the `strict'
	  branch.

2002-03-25 Monday 19:40  Roberto Bagnara <bagnara@cs.unipr.it>

	* interfaces/C/: ppl_c.cc (1.11), ppl_c.h (1.12): More interface
	  functions added.

