2002-03-10 Sunday 21:14  Roberto Bagnara <bagnara@cs.unipr.it>

	* src/: Row.cc (1.29), Row.defs.hh (1.31): Avoid the creation of
	  temporaries in operator*(const Row& x, const Row& y).  This
	  results in a speedup of at least 3%.

